Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.12,0:07:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不妙...非常不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
