Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話今年夏天的無眠之夜要持續下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可夠糟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.63,0:11:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.52,0:11:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳得這麼沸沸揚揚 逃是逃不掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.16,0:11:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也去求拓海跑一趟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.68,0:11:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可對手是32 就算拓海也難以對付啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.64,0:11:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且Night Kids的中裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.66,0:11:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是與高橋兄弟同級別的有名車手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.45,0:11:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艱難的比賽 好像毫無勝算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一想 也不好硬求他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.27,0:12:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂...老爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,32很厲害嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.74,0:12:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,32嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實挺厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.07,0:12:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老爸的話下山能贏32嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.69,0:12:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能贏 不管32還是別的車都不在話下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.83,0:12:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的話...能贏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.89,0:12:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道 勝負一線間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.53,0:12:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼問這個? 要和32比?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.20,0:12:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏 只是隨便問問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.87,0:12:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著是32嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.90,0:13:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,86的設定稍微差了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.32,0:13:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝負一線間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.10,0:13:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我感覺這個時間來的話就能見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.94,0:14:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為初次見面也是這個時間段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.56,0:14:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要和Night Kids的中裏比嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.11,0:14:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的事附近傳得沸沸揚揚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.87,0:14:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先聲明 我可不記得我有說過要和32比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.99,0:14:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受挑戰時我並不在場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以毫無興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫無興趣是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.21,0:14:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Night Kids的中裏不是指名挑戰的你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.94,0:14:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那接受不就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.01,0:14:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把他痛扁一頓 你應該能行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.43,0:14:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼那麼說 又和你無關...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.75,0:14:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然有關 因為你贏了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.49,0:14:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能贏你的只可能是REDSUNS的高橋兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.84,0:14:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前絕不能輸 就算對手是32
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.74,0:14:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說了我不比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.15,0:15:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且也沒理由去比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,理由? 什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車手參加比賽需要理由嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.72,0:15:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又不是車手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.89,0:15:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是在諷刺我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.74,0:15:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有那樣的技術應該經過了大量的訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.39,0:15:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想當車手的人為什麼會經常訓練?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是喜歡才去開車的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.64,0:15:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是幫家裏送貨而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.50,0:15:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別撒謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.93,0:15:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勉勉強強地開車怎麼可能擁那麼厲害的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.36,0:15:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是那樣 你不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不明白的是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.68,0:15:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭開車的人會精通漂移之類的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.64,0:15:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是真心喜歡的話絕對無法擁有那種技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.89,0:15:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可能自己都沒察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.69,0:15:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但內心絕對是喜歡駕駛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著 只要喜歡開車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.87,0:16:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是個合格的車手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.50,0:16:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車手的話就會對自己領悟出的技術感到驕傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.56,0:16:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受別人的挑戰也是車手的驕傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.95,0:16:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,枉我特地來見你 真失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.66,0:16:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能自己都沒察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但內心是喜歡駕駛的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.41,0:16:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...被挑戰就必須接受 這算什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是無法接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.01,0:16:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,樹 拓海呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.92,0:16:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天晚班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.62,0:16:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.92,0:16:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.65,0:17:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今晚去秋名山向Night Kids的中裏道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,樹...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.23,0:17:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跪下或者怎麼都行 說出實情的話或許會原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.44,0:17:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且本來就與SPEED STARS無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.15,0:17:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知能否說服拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.38,0:17:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得沒希望 我很清楚他的性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.83,0:17:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他極其討厭別人強迫或命令他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.46,0:17:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外表很沉默 可一旦話出口就變得很頑固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.77,0:17:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這性格像極了他老爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.54,0:17:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被挑戰就要接受是車手默認的規則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.70,0:17:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但拓海無法理解所以很排斥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.24,0:17:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強行挑戰的話他就會拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.19,0:17:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小子二年級時就和足球部的前輩翻過臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.43,0:17:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海居然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.07,0:18:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店長 外面都收拾好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.72,0:18:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.52,0:18:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.15,0:18:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.65,0:18:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來這坐一會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.93,0:18:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.68,0:18:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的 我偶然聽到件事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.71,0:18:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚好像要和32比賽吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.67,0:18:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是放棄的好 對手太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.16,0:18:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...這件事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.33,0:18:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說了 之前的事你不說我也清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都不出我的所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.16,0:18:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道那是在你不情願的情況下接受的比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.38,0:18:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是樹得意忘形之下接受的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可你人太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.63,0:19:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為保朋友的面子不得不去應付吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別怪我說話難聽 32的話還是放棄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.56,0:19:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不太熟悉車 不知道32是怎樣的車吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.04,0:19:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,32...有那麼厲害?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好極 上鉤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.41,0:19:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經不能用厲害來形容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.49,0:19:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一點很特別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.74,0:19:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它有著結合了FR和四驅優點的驅動系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.33,0:19:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾乎是犯規的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,86和GTR有天壤之別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.59,0:19:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車手差勁的話還能比比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可對方也是相當有名的車手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.40,0:19:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和老爸說的不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.88,0:19:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他明明說是勝負一線間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在聽嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.31,0:19:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易在與赤城車隊的交流戰中取勝 名氣大增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是慎重點好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.69,0:20:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和沒有勝算的對手比 不是聰明的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.54,0:20:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.44,0:20:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對手是32 我想不應戰也沒人會說你逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.88,0:20:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.29,0:20:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.68,0:20:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝特意忠告 但很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並沒想過要作為車手來沽名釣譽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.41,0:20:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這又不是什麼大事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何都不放棄嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.79,0:20:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.25,0:20:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被說得那麼厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.78,0:20:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這車到底有多厲害 無論如何要見識一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.03,0:20:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不怕32什麼的 告辭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.14,0:20:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和他父親的反應一樣精彩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.37,0:21:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臨時休業?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.09,0:21:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.12,0:21:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼窮了還不好好工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.14,0:21:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,槽了 車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.85,0:21:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去喝酒的話就沒希望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.92,0:21:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到早上才會回來 可惡的老爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.12,0:21:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒車的話全都是空話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.84,0:21:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該早上就跟他借車的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.92,0:21:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好多觀眾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.10,0:21:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比上次和赤城交流戰時更熱鬧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.84,0:21:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼多人 究竟想來看什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.61,0:21:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肯定不是32
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.52,0:21:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是為了看86的漂移
